{"tid":2340862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大「肢解」中共史研究中心  主任不滿無諮詢劈炮 校方否認受壓","createTime":"2020-12-26T00:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:18:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c4b4d28e450e2388164e7c687caaf219dcdab4","tid":2340862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:33:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/I5Z43IEMXBB7JDSQCGCY64CWJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FI5Z43IEMXBB7JDSQCGCY64CWJA%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=8009d2fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FI5Z43IEMXBB7JDSQCGCY64CWJA%2F&h=50fa2735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/I5Z43IEMXBB7JDSQCGCY64CWJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中大「肢解」中共史研究中心 <br />\n主任不滿無諮詢劈炮 校方否認受壓<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港中文大學明年改組有逾50年歷史、收藏大量中國史料的中國研究服務中心，內容以中共建政後國情及民情為主的館藏，將會悉數交由大學圖書館管理。據悉，中心其中一名主任李磊（Pierre F. Landry）因校方未就改組事宜諮詢他，於改組前憤而離職。消息人士形容，校方此舉變相將中心「解體」，或與中心早年與美方關係密切有關。中大否認有關說法，辯稱改組一事絕非受外部壓力影響。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：西方學者創立 藏文革 大饑荒 史料<br />\n<br />\n中國研究服務中心另。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tZN3el_oToNXCaEGdMDJBEkizTM=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V2ZHBUN4HZDBXKXVBLPWQLWT7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtZN3el_oToNXCaEGdMDJBEkizTM%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV2ZHBUN4HZDBXKXVBLPWQLWT7Y.jpg&h=2d203384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中心主任趙志裕向職員交代改組計劃，館藏將悉數交由大學圖書館管理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「千人計劃」特聘專家助重組<br />\n<br />\n趙志裕證實，李磊已提出辭去中心主任一職，。。。。。。。。。。。。。趙志裕身兼中大社會科學院院長，也是中國「千人計劃」特聘專家。<br />\n<br />\n有消息人士向本報透露，中研中心多年來在中國研究界享負盛名，校方將其併入大學圖書館，變相是將中心解體。據他了解，校方的重組計劃可謂「由上而下、封閉」，事前未曾諮詢李磊以及中心的國際顧問委員會。該委員會向來是中心的重要組成部份，今年逝世的知名學者傅高義（Ezra F. Vogel）曾在1992年至2015年間出任此委員會主席。<br />\n<br />\n趙志裕回應本報查詢。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n信件表示，改。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳健民曾掌舵 被屈間諜中心<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。加上「佔中三子」之一的陳健民在2014年雨傘運動時曾任中心主任，成為被整頓的矛頭。<br />\n<br />\n中文大學發表。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xV_dzFrDf8n-ellDa284kFrvKUk=/844x1575/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YJG7EWWIWJABLJDECGKIIIACRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxV_dzFrDf8n-ellDa284kFrvKUk%3D%2F844x1575%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYJG7EWWIWJABLJDECGKIIIACRQ.jpg&h=52150540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙志裕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s_NfpyrgvVAude3eMiNQ_PXRFeU=/639x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2LCDWD5W3ZEZDORV5NO7YGXK5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs_NfpyrgvVAude3eMiNQ_PXRFeU%3D%2F639x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2LCDWD5W3ZEZDORV5NO7YGXK5Y.jpg&h=a9f9dff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■因未獲校方諮詢改組事宜，中心其中一名主任李磊憤而離職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6v2csbksil0XmXchbtTyIuBIsZA=/671x385/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IJ2E5GUCCFHCLBBTVLPU3NTTIE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6v2csbksil0XmXchbtTyIuBIsZA%3D%2F671x385%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIJ2E5GUCCFHCLBBTVLPU3NTTIE.gif&h=678ca43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■知名學者傅高義（左圖）及陳健民（右圖）先後於中心擔任要職。"},{"pid":"9dc87a698f1df188add67a2387c86a7e0ab43e94","tid":2340862,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de819c19f300000bab54860f621f5f54eeb0fc9","tid":2340862,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bb33d185f7a76d871327ec5c27e0f538bb1c07","tid":2340862,"uid":337210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T00:58:39.000Z","msg":"死段狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9875e08b939ae4a11f4561187e693df9c671ffd2","tid":2340862,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ4qLJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ4qLJ0.jpg&h=69f445df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"938ed20742ef72237094500a1720e5cd38254b80","tid":2340862,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"屌⋯⋯"},{"pid":"3b7e6ddfdaa465b3136565246307313e6cc2c132","tid":2340862,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a096ce3ae83b98ce7eec1c6af6315d1049d861","tid":2340862,"uid":259520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"想將中共D黑歷史刪除!!<br />\n<br />\n習近平要篡改歷史 中大中國研究服務中心凍過水 黃世澤幾分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QV-BNlxBMSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQV-BNlxBMSM&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=48353ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QV-BNlxBMSM</a>"},{"pid":"a7a6ea5c8915190db8618fd101bfcd7370db99be","tid":2340862,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">將全部館藏，資料俾上 LBRY </span></span>"},{"pid":"e52f371510f0c3a4cdaba70202188ff014d56f53","tid":2340862,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/lxB0Qj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FlxB0Qj.gif&h=e04c2b1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"396f30a0292fea1cc782fd80e805629a902c9274","tid":2340862,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"要改寫共匪D黑歷史，唔意外。"},{"pid":"ee81108943b053a757cf33d1b5aa0f7d64a32e0a","tid":2340862,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:18:30.000Z","msg":"中國當代政治運動史數據庫系列<br />\n1.《中國文化大革命數據庫（1966-1976）》，2002-2006年出版，包括了1965-1981年的所有政治運動。<br />\n2.《中國反右運動數據庫（1957-）》，2010年出版，涵蓋了自1955-1958年的政治運動。<br />\n3.《中國大躍進&mdash;&mdash;大饑荒數據庫（1958-1964）》，2013年出版，將包括在這一期間的所有政治經濟風雲。<br />\n4.《中國五十年代初中期運動數據庫（1949-1955）》，計劃在2014-2015年出版，將包括土地改革、思想改造、農業、手工業和工商業改造在內的所有政治運動。"}]}